{"tid":364971,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【基金啟示】炒美股嘅朋友 兩張不能不看的名單！","createTime":"2017-08-18T23:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T07:19:23.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce58008a2462a160c91f8673894cb499365b117","tid":364971,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T23:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170816/large/1502851140_ee35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170816%2Flarge%2F1502851140_ee35.jpg&h=47e15f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170816/large/1502851168_d8af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170816%2Flarge%2F1502851168_d8af.png&h=8b780f42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對沖基金第二季掃得最狼名單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170816/large/1502851170_4a15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170816%2Flarge%2F1502851170_4a15.png&h=d830f8ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對沖基金第二季沽得最狠名單<br />\n<br />\n對沖基金陸續公佈投資報告，基金第二季愛股名單亦已出爐！據彭博引述監管文件報道，第二季獲對沖基金湧有最多資金的股份為Altaba。Yahoo早前出售核心電訊資產予Verizon，餘下公司已正式改名為Altaba，Altaba亦為控制著Yahoo所持的阿里巴巴股份。至於阿里巴巴，則位列榜單第四。<br />\n<br />\n投資市場「愛恨分明」，第二季被基金沖得最甘股份為Facebook，被減持規模達到26億美元。出售Facebook最多的是Viking Global Investors。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57086928&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57086928%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170816&d=jKMfaIENg%2FsepRZOusneR3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e0b33744\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57086928%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170816&h=9dc90108\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57086928&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170816</a>"},{"pid":"4284639dace267321ede3b7bc51b1b2123d031b3","tid":364971,"uid":68821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:54:54.000Z","msg":"BABA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6149b6e467458bbdb12d54bd722cd07671ba19b2","tid":364971,"uid":129507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"baba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5918d08455e20af14f961e17722ee424a62b0ba","tid":364971,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:13:55.000Z","msg":"點解會睇淡autodesk PayPal <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd61bf7d4cac08d66e7badb3be01f8afcc139c24","tid":364971,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:10:46.000Z","msg":"但現在已經就來第三個quarter"},{"pid":"4510792afa87b87058af38dfd2869706fb1540ba","tid":364971,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會睇淡autodesk PayPal <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPypl 我相信係個競爭太大，有一個SQ已經好大壓力"},{"pid":"899423b4d604812f8d20b9997747b798ad26cbe2","tid":364971,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"D E Shaw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}